('CWI', 'codes_standards', 'Per AWS D1.1, what is the minimum prequalification requirement for a Welder Performance Qualification?', 'Visual inspection only', 'Mechanical testing or radiographic testing per §6', 'Owner approval only', 'No testing required', 'B', 'AWS D1.1 §6 requires WPQ to be supported by mechanical testing (bend tests) or RT depending on the qualification range.', 'AWS D1.1 §6.18', 'hard'),
